Subject: [PATCH 100/122] Revert "mm: replace VM_LOCKED_CLEAR_MASK with
 VM_LOCKED_MASK"

This reverts commit 4b0c1a34f5f5c2654637b0507d7a94958690921b.

Signed-off-by: Piotr Gorski <lucjan.lucjanov@gmail.com>
---
 include/linux/mm.h | 4 ++--
 kernel/fork.c      | 2 +-
 mm/hugetlb.c       | 4 ++--
 mm/mlock.c         | 6 +++---
 mm/mmap.c          | 6 +++---
